# ============================================================
# hello.kid  -  KidLang Sample Program 01
# Topic: Hello World - First Program
# ============================================================

# Print a welcome message
SHOW "Hello, World!"
SHOW "Welcome to KidLang!"
SHOW "This is your first program."

# Print a blank line
SHOW ""

# Print some numbers
SHOW "Let us count to 5:"
SHOW 1
SHOW 2
SHOW 3
SHOW 4
SHOW 5

SHOW ""
SHOW "Great job! You ran your first KidLang program!"
